import sys
sys.stdin = open("input.txt", "r")
n = int(input())
f = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
# print(f)
for i in range(n):
    if f[i] == 0:
        for j in range(1, n+1):
            if j not in f and j != i:
                f[i] = j
                break
print(*f)
